‚úçÔ∏è How to Author the Component Step-by-Step
Drag & Drop the Component into your page from the component browser.

Open Dialog, go to the Properties tab:

Style Type ‚Üí Choose one of:

Summary: Full card with benefits, CTA, rewards

Compare Tile: For table-style compare view

Compare Banner: Narrow horizontal layout

Compare Add: Compact layout with "Add to compare"

